{"tid":1153431,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 太陽の都 - 日系畫風 奇幻冒險 MMORPG！23/5 配信開始！","createTime":"2019-05-13T15:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T07:10:29.000Z","uid":66923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"249dd3dc4681b2705e7e47d0a22cf5a78db7622b","tid":1153431,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wAmryYw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwAmryYw.jpg&h=d88ca251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方網站 : <a href=\"https://mxtw.originmood.com/event/20190501/?sou=post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmxtw.originmood.com%2Fevent%2F20190501%2F%3Fsou%3Dpost&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=502ef68b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mxtw.originmood.com/event/20190501/?sou=post</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/OriginMood.TYZD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOriginMood.TYZD%2F&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=e0f71243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/OriginMood.TYZD/</a><br />\nYouTube : <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8-jHfnW2Zic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8-jHfnW2Zic&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b47f3bdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8-jHfnW2Zic</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲簡介</span></span></strong><br />\n 《太陽之都》這款大世界冒險MMORPG手機遊戲，日前由初心網絡科技股份有限公司 （ORIGIN MOOD LIMITED）宣佈取得台港澳獨家代理權，並將在台港澳地區全球首發。<br />\n<br />\n原本的世界欣欣向榮，直至那場災厄降臨<br />\n在已被遺忘的時代，有一個崇尚生命的國度，太陽之都。子民順應天命安分守己。王子企圖用魔法實現永恆統治，卻被邪惡能量侵蝕。繼而殃及子民，被黑魔法變成瘋狂的怪物。或許觸怒了真正的神明，王宮無故沉入地底。千百年來，餘下怪物依然在外遊蕩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGyEUeK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGyEUeK.jpg&h=208cec21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貴族認為王宮下沉是神諭，他們不能隨便處置那些人類變成的怪物。可埋藏於王宮廢墟中的寶藏吸引了眾多冒險者，他們無視警告肅清怪物。關於對待怪物的態度使兩方分歧越來越大，最終形成兩大勢力，雙方水火不容。<br />\n<br />\n而災禍的根源，王子，其實一直覬覦著世界，正伺機打開連接的大門一舉反攻。太陽之都的矛盾與命運，能否被前來的勇者拯救......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhfWWh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhfWWh2.jpg&h=d4673ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲特色</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">冒險物語傳頌的大世界，傳承神諭的魔法大地</span></span></strong><br />\n《太陽之都》擁有宏大的世界觀及體系架構，遊戲中每一處的場景都如夢幻般舒坦，廣闊的荒野、深邃的監獄、灼熱的火山、漆黑的幽谷，隱秘的遺跡，燈紅的旅館。從角色創建到進入主要城市，遊戲中的每個細節都完美呈現，讓玩家感覺自己真實處於這個大世界之中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umSa0MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumSa0MA.jpg&h=0a0bb6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJOQ0Mj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJOQ0Mj.jpg&h=3e7cdd74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《太陽之都》整體風格採用了類似油墨紙的畫面質感以及營造復古感的泛黃色調。濃厚日系感覺，細膩遊戲場景具有歷史感，視覺表達非常亮眼。每一幅場景、每一個物件、每一名角色都似乎帶著自己的經歷站在你的面前。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCxiqdw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCxiqdw.jpg&h=96a87412&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rAH2RTw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrAH2RTw.jpg&h=4c07664b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5AZHRTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5AZHRTx.jpg&h=4dfd50c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">日語原聲NPC，譜奏太陽下遺失的心靈之光</span></span></strong><br />\n冒險家與遊戲中登場的角色皆存在不一樣的契約。遊戲中每一位NPC，不僅擁有完善獨立的人物設定，每一位NPC都擁有自己的背景故事，性格特點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bx35PNi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbx35PNi.jpg&h=8290b652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L8yp5dV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL8yp5dV.jpg&h=38556645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LjqTd7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLjqTd7g.jpg&h=35a4adf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82gfssg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82gfssg.jpg&h=40c107eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHrK5dX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHrK5dX.jpg&h=2516a389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">最初的旅人 與 運命的守護精靈</span></span></strong><br />\n夢寐的牽絆，可愛的守護精靈，在天空的藍耀下，眷屬於不同的旅人。我們簽訂契約，伴隨著旅程的歷練，無數的幻化與成長。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2bWb2y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2bWb2y.png&h=b2a1a42c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大地的詠嘆詩 高潔的勇者誓言 魔法與劍的交織力量</span></span></strong><br />\n以聖劍破除混沌，以魔法冰結大海，詠唱着大地的生靈，療癒冒險的傷痕。多重轉職與分支，我們謹守職業與公會的戰鬥崗位，交織出撼動大地的夥伴力量。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲中一共有6種職業：初期3大職業（傭兵、術士、射手），一轉時有各有2個轉職方向。男女角色均可選擇任意職業。<br />\n傭兵：戰爭之影、神之門徒<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">技能展示 :</span></strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2272822192810568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2272822192810568&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=a5c90bb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2272822192810568</a><br />\n術士：自然先知、亡域之主<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">技能展示 :</span></strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2425904967632216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2425904967632216&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b904641c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2425904967632216</a><br />\n射手：科技使徒、狩魔使徒<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">技能展示 :</span></strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=847940088889656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D847940088889656&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=0ef5c32a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=847940088889656</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHXiqnW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHXiqnW.jpg&h=e4663c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nrmCFWk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnrmCFWk.jpg&h=39115203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">台港澳全球首發，事前登錄開跑！</span></span></strong><br />\n《太陽之都》日前已經開放事前登錄，全城響起啟程冒險的號角，永不遺忘的勇者之心，勇者們集結出發，載滿幸福的冒險與期待。官方後續將持續為大家搶先公開更多遊戲相關資訊及活動，請鎖定《太陽之都》官方網站，掌握第一手資訊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y42VssB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy42VssB.jpg&h=01b6c483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8j5oBxy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8j5oBxy.jpg&h=d4104d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 主題曲</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9Ka_nc_NUk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_9Ka_nc_NUk&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=fe3677e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9Ka_nc_NUk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲圖片</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JFRxcbVZlss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJFRxcbVZlss&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=1e48ed3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JFRxcbVZlss</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kfTd8P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kfTd8P.jpg&h=e1f70374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMhVst7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMhVst7.jpg&h=7666c650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKTmn2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKTmn2s.jpg&h=283db750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNM7iAN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNM7iAN.jpg&h=95f88391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yG1K5fO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyG1K5fO.jpg&h=fa82eafd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTDET88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTDET88.jpg&h=167a97a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">事前登錄：</span></div></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://mxtw.originmood.com/event/20190501/?sou=newstw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmxtw.originmood.com%2Fevent%2F20190501%2F%3Fsou%3Dnewstw&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=ae681822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mxtw.originmood.com/event/20190501/?sou=newstw</a></div></span></strong> 《太陽之都》事前登錄活動已經火熱展開，立刻參加事前登錄即可在遊戲上市後享受多項好禮：金幣、珍貴素材、坐騎以及只能從事前登錄獲得的限定精靈。只要於活動頁面填寫手機號碼參加登錄，就能獲得坐騎陸行鳥，參與祈願再得地區限定精靈「寶冠松鼠」和「巨劍黑熊」二選一。 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BdoxuK8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdoxuK8.jpg&h=3f8bec4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqWWbYu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqWWbYu.jpg&h=7b6d4776&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DScRLh7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDScRLh7.jpg&h=2ac0d366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSDtNwZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSDtNwZ.jpg&h=a5271171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS：<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1458722444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fid1458722444&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=3c08ff79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1458722444</a><br />\nAndroid：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.originmood.mxtw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.originmood.mxtw&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=1b99c778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.originmood.mxtw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/7843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F7843&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=6af35ea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/7843</a>"},{"pid":"b92403eea9e2239d9e699aa787be25cc2bdb97af","tid":1153431,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 職業介紹</span></span></strong><br />\n遊戲中一共有6種職業：初期3大職業（傭兵、術士、射手），一轉時有各有2個轉職方向。男女角色均可選擇任意職業。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">傭兵：戰爭之影、神之門徒</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">技能展示 : </span></strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2272822192810568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2272822192810568&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=a5c90bb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2272822192810568</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1.戰爭之影</span></strong><br />\n武器：槍<br />\n簡介：嗜戰如狂的猛士，將搏殺融入自己的生命，狂熱無比<br />\n技能<br />\n槍擊：擊退技，群體擊退，震盪乾坤，進可攻退可守；<br />\n狂熱：持續技，持續傷害，席捲八荒，掃清六合；<br />\n乘勝追擊：傷害技，高傷害技，乘勝追擊，直搗黃龍；<br />\n怒火：控制技，爆裂重擊，群體擊暈，扭轉戰局替；<br />\n戰火臨世：終極技，引槍入天，神槍入地，造成毀滅打擊。<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.神之門徒</span></strong><br />\n武器：劍盾<br />\n簡介：侍奉神明的光明戰士，以正義為劍，以聖光為盾，裁決不公，阻絕黑暗<br />\n技能<br />\n洗禮:傷害技，天降神祗，願聖光洗禮驅除邪惡，撫平創傷。<br />\n割裂:傷害技，讓負罪之血滋養大地，重立秩序。<br />\n聖堂:擊飛技，以聖堂之力，融入血脈，重創惡敵。<br />\n淨化:控制技，一切黑暗化為灰燼，喚光明普渡眾生。<br />\n神聖之劍:終極技，以神之名，光芒為劍，斬斷罪惡之源。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">術士：自然先知、亡域之主</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">技能展示 : </span></strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2425904967632216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2425904967632216&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b904641c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2425904967632216</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1.自然先知</span></strong><br />\n武器：法杖<br />\n簡介：沉浸元素之秘的優秀法師，最善用冰、火兩種元素，給予敵人沉重打擊。<br />\n技能<br />\n冰雪之怒:擊飛技，凜冬烈風，冰雪咆哮，領教自然之怒。<br />\n冰錐:傷害技，突如其來的地下冰錐，刺破鎧甲與勇氣。<br />\n火雨:持續技，烈焰風暴，焚盡罪業。<br />\n烈焰噴湧:控制技，洶湧岩漿，將一切生命融成灰。<br />\n龍之吐息:終極技，以古咒呼喚龍炎，席捲大地，遮蔽天空。<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.亡域之主</span></strong><br />\n武器：權杖、盾<br />\n簡介：崇尚亡靈之力的古怪巫師，用黑魔法喚醒沉眠死者，重創膽敢為敵的無知者。<br />\n技能<br />\n死者問候:持續技，持續傷害，喚醒沉眠的亡靈，襲殺敵人。<br />\n毒液煉獄:傷害技，以劇毒融合魔法，腐蝕大地與生靈。<br />\n骨龍蘇醒:擊飛技，借助骨龍之力，將一切忤逆之意化齏粉。<br />\n殘暴幽靈:控制技，與亡靈士兵簽訂契約，震悚來犯之敵。<br />\n巫蠱之神:終極技，彙聚巫蠱魔力，否極泰來，終將成神。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">射手：科技使徒、狩魔使徒</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">技能展示 : </span></strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=847940088889656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D847940088889656&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=0ef5c32a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=847940088889656</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1.科技使徒</span></strong><br />\n武器：弩（後期拿槍炮）<br />\n簡介：以弩為口，以矢為語，誅盡宵小，蕩平乾坤。<br />\n技能<br />\n鋸齒矢:多段技，鋸齒輪盤，割裂陣線，不留活口。<br />\n強擊弩:持續技，蓄力重擊，破甲斷兵，所向披靡。<br />\n擴散彈:延時技，爆裂散射，以一敵百，萬夫不當。<br />\n落雷:控制技，以箭為媒，溝通天域，降雷，淨世。<br />\n雷池天罰:終極技，污穢太多，淨土太少，願以雷罰，重塑磊落。<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.狩魔使徒</span></strong><br />\n武器：弓<br />\n簡介：隱藏於陰影中的黑色死神，用無聲之息收割者一個又一個的生命。<br />\n技能：<br />\n箭雨沼澤:持續技，箭雨瞬發，落地沼澤，殞命難行。<br />\n透甲箭:擊飛技，直線貫穿，透甲破壁，縱銅牆鐵壁不敢近。<br />\n黑暗之力:傷害技，以黑暗之力附著弓箭，撕碎憎惡之敵。<br />\n驟雨:控制技，震盪波箭，群體射暈，關鍵無可取代。<br />\n冥神之吻:終極技，死神代言人降臨世間，凡人皆須一死。"},{"pid":"7195f00df68042bb3a569938ba571ec7163a3ba6","tid":1153431,"uid":12207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"好似pc隻救世者之樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e9b3c04eebb323858d6da8a198817097d65b4f","tid":1153431,"uid":7483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"改名番兜左幾轉既舊game黎"},{"pid":"fe63e21687910c793567d2650344a6c669ab97ff","tid":1153431,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22e9b3c04eebb323858d6da8a198817097d65b4f","tid":1153431,"uid":7483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"改名番兜左幾轉既舊game黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class